invariant functools_extra196.lru_cache_name_eq:
  description: "functools.lru_cache.__name__.__eq__('lru_cache') == True — lru_cache is a Python-level decorator function; __name__ is 'lru_cache' (len=9); verified with Python 3.14.3; new to extra196"
  category: identity
